    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Yes, you can get it from the <a href=\"http://docs.oracle.com/javase/7/docs/api/java/io/File.html\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><code>File</code></a> object by using <a href=\"http://docs.oracle.com/javase/7/docs/api/java/io/File.html#toPath()\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><code>File.toPath()</code></a>. Keep in mind that this is only for Java 7+. Java versions 6 and below do not have it.</p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 50566,
      "reputation" : 9984,
      "user_id" : 150884,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "accept_rate" : 83,
      "profile_image" : "https://i.sstatic.net/5vmQJ.jpg?s=256",
