  "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/questions/15512200/get-java-nio-file-path-object-from-java-io-file",
  "title" : "Get java.nio.file.Path object from java.io.File",
  "body" : "<p>Is it possible to get a Path object from a <code>java.io.File</code>?</p>\n\n<p>I know you can convert a path to a file using <code>toFile()</code> method, but I couldn't find the opposite conversion. Is there a way to do this in Java 6 or lower?</p>\n"
